<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <% include head %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/lib/suimobile/sm.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/phone/css/index.css">
</head>
<body ng-app="webapp">
<div class="content" id="login">
    <header>
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="/phone/images/logo.png" >
            汇中微交易直播平台
        </div>
    </header>
    <section ng-controller="UserController">
        <form  class="login-form">
            <div class="form-input"><input type="text" placeholder="请输入手机号码" name="phone" ng-model="phone"></div>
            <div class="clearfix">
                <div class="form-input pull-left" style="width:62%"><input type="text" placeholder="手机验证码" name="checkCode" ng-model="checkCode"><input type="hidden" name="sendCode"  ng-model="sendCode" ></div>
                <div class="form-input get-check-code pull-right" style="width:36%"><input type="button"  ng-click="getCheckCode()" ng-value="val" ng-class="ing"  ng-disabled="disabled"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="prompt">
                <p>您可能需要1分钟左右才会收到验证码。 </p>
                <p>请勿向任何人透露此验证码。</p>
                <p>如果没收到，请重新获取验证码</p>
            </div>
            <div class="form-input login-submit "><input type="button" value="登录" ng-click="login()"></div>
            <input type="hidden" name="userid" ng-init="id='<%=id%>'" >
            <input type="hidden" name="wx" ng-init="wx='<%=wx%>'" >
        </form>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <p>© 亿数达网络科技有限公司版权所有</p>
    </footer>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/phone/dist/index.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>